✅ **Configuration**: The Analytics component is already properly configured in the root layout file.

✅ **Additional Features**: The project also includes `@vercel/speed-insights` (v2.0.0) for performance monitoring.

## Implementation Details

### File: `src/app/layout.tsx`

The Analytics component is correctly imported and placed in the root layout:

```typescript
import { Analytics } from '@vercel/analytics/next'
import { SpeedInsights } from '@vercel/speed-insights/next'

// ... inside the body tag
<body>
  <ProgressMerger />
  {children}
  <Analytics />
  <SpeedInsights />
</body>
```

This follows the latest Vercel documentation from https://vercel.com/docs/analytics/quickstart for Next.js App Router projects.

