## Next Steps

To enable analytics data collection on Vercel:
1. Navigate to your Vercel dashboard
2. Select your project
3. Go to Analytics in the sidebar
4. Click the "Enable" button
5. Deploy the application to production

Analytics data will start appearing in your dashboard after deployment and visitor activity.

## Framework Compatibility

- **Framework**: Next.js 16.2.6 (App Router)
- **Package Manager**: npm
- **Analytics Package**: @vercel/analytics@2.0.1
- **Speed Insights**: @vercel/speed-insights@2.0.0

The implementation is up-to-date with the latest Vercel Analytics best practices for Next.js App Router projects.
